description:
New carpeting and freshly painted out, this two bedroom condo style apartment is ready for occupancy June 1'st. Large kitchen, half bath, living room, laundry closet downstairs and two large bedrooms with ample closet space and full bath upstairs. Nice patio off the kitchen to set up your grill or enjoy your morning coffee. Stay toasty warm this winter with efficient Rinnai propane heater. Washer/ dryer hookup and off street parking for two vehicles. Owner provides plowing and trash removal, tenants responsible for all other utilities.
Extremely convenient location, walking distance to La Habra Police Department, downtown La Habra AND Shopping Center. Security deposit, background and credit screening mandatory for incoming tenants. Please contact THE APARTMENT CONNECTION for additional information and for viewing. ....  show contact info
